have a drink,

40:21.839 --> 40:23.090
celebrate with your family.

40:23.090 --> 40:24.800
With my family.

40:24.800 --> 40:26.426
Uh, good.

40:26.426 --> 40:29.721
Uh, well, uh, goodbye.

40:29.721 --> 40:31.598
If, if you get anything wrong,
I'll call you.

40:31.598 --> 40:34.685
I'm expecting you to. Goodnight.

40:36.687 --> 40:38.564
Oh yes.

40:38.939 --> 40:41.567
Yes! Yes! Yes!

40:45.195 --> 40:47.489
Oh! Good!

40:47.948 --> 40:48.991
Yes!

40:52.995 --> 40:54.955
Ahh.

40:56.039 --> 40:57.374
Oh good.

40:59.251 --> 41:00.544
That's done.

41:14.975 --> 41:17.019
Hi. Could have a glass of water, please?

41:20.063 --> 41:21.481
A whiskey with ice.

41:28.155 --> 41:30.407
