41:38.916 --> 41:40.250
It is an honor.

41:40.250 --> 41:42.544
- Yeah, it is good to see you--

41:42.544 --> 41:44.755
- I'm looking forward to reading
the article in the <i>Journal.</i>

41:45.214 --> 41:46.673
Yes, I know about it.

41:46.673 --> 41:49.009
I think a lot of people
will be interested in it.

41:50.302 --> 41:53.597
And when this becomes a scandal,
because it will become a scandal,

41:53.597 --> 41:56.600
what do you think happens
to all of the other women

41:56.600 --> 41:58.227
who want to start companies?

41:59.394 --> 42:00.604
Who do they go to?

42:01.897 --> 42:03.524
Who's going to trust them?

42:05.192 --> 42:06.485
Because it's not just you.

42:08.779 --> 42:10.072
It's never just you.

42:12.366 --> 42:14.034
It was good to see you, Phyllis.

42:14.034 --> 42:15.869
- Don't call me Phyllis.
I'm not Phyllis to you.

42:15.869 --> 42:16.995
I'm Dr. Gardner.

42:53.699 --> 42:55.450
<i>You know,
I realized something last night.</i>

42:57.202 --> 42:58.328
This is what happens.

42:59.997 --> 43:02.499
This is what happens
when you work to change things.

43:02.499 --> 43:04.501
<i>First, they think you're crazy.</i>

43:05.544 --> 43:06.503
